Libseq C++ Bio sequence library
-------------------------------

Requirements
------------

* cmake (www.cmake.org)
* C++ environment

Build instructions
------------------

Create a temporary build directory (for example within the project root)

$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ../
$ make

To build the simple test programs
---------------------------------

(Inside the build directory:)

$ cd test
$ make

To install
----------

$ make install

To create the documentation
---------------------------

(In the project root)

$ doxygen

